title: Juju Eats
typeOfFood: American, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A salad restaurant with several outlets (see webpage). Offers an extensive menu of a la carte salads, as well as do-it-yourself salads, wraps, cold press juices, cold brew juices, and fresh fruit sodas. Also offers juice cleanse drinks. This one is situated 5 minutes from the main shopping area in Greenbelt.
streetAddress: 2297 Chino Roces Avenue Extension, G/F BCS Building
